These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: drawing, reading
Job: paramedic, social-worker
1. Job:paramedic is in an even position##4
2. Job:social-worker == Hobby:reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | reading | drawing |
| Job     | social-worker    | paramedic   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: milk, tea
Sport: swimming, parkour
1. Sport:swimming is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:tea is on the left of Beverage:milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | tea | milk        |
| Sport      | swimming  | parkour |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: punk, salsa
Nationality: british, american
1. Nationality:british is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | punk |
| Nationality   | british | american |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
